content:encoded:
This week we sit down with the wonderful Chef Uyen Kirshenbaum, to discuss the small business she started after being furloughed from her restaurant job due to COVID-19. We're also talking about how she succeeded in starting a business during a global pandemic how her peers in the restaurant industry have been able to adapt, her biggest hardships, and advice for those looking to invest in their own ideas.
